0.0.4
=====
*	requires twisted >= 11.1.0, since there is heartbeat support

*	introduced -V argument

0.0.3
=====
*	PyPi packaging

0.0.2
=====
*	Config format for main.channels changed from ", " separated to just space
	separated

*	No more XDG, path to config is specified by -c argument

*	Redirbot does not start without any arguments or with -h|--help anymore

*	some log messages have changed

*	Using ReconnectingClientFactory
